{
  "stem": "27507.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The only thing that I remember is that my father would on the Yom Kippur, which is about the only day that I am-- that I really remember that he took part-- that he went to the synagogue-- the main synagogue in Warsaw, which was in Tlomackiem, which was a big impressive building.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But it was a kind of a most-- how should I put it?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Most unorthodox-- no unorthodox.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was orthodox, of course, but it was the more progressive type of synagogue in Warsaw, the one to which those Jews went who had-- who didn't belong permanently to a small synagogue where they would be coming practically almost every day.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that one was-- I think people were coming there more at high holy days and so on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he went there on Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's what I remember, but other than that, hardly.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the other vocations or anything else that you remember from your life?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Did you go on vacations or stay?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We went.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We went but before the war, we went to-- well, we must have gone to near Warsaw as well.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we went to the sea almost every year, to Sopot which is-- which is near Gdansk, near Danzig on the Baltic Sea.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was a well-known-- well-known resort-- and we spent-- we went there, I think, more or less every year.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "At least, I remember in 19-- probably 1937-- and probably as well in 1938 and one would-- one would rent a room or a number of rooms there and stay there for this in the summer, usually for probably for at least a month or maybe even two months.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Usually one went, because after the war, we still continued going to Sopot.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
